<h1 class="dark:text-gray-500 font-bold text-4xl">New auction item</h1>
<hr class='my-4' />
<div class='flex gap-[50px] w-full'>
  <div class='dark:bg-slate-700 bg-white p-8 rounded-xl w-full dark:text-white'>
    <div class="mb-4 font-medium text-2xl">About starting an auction</div>
    <ul class='list-disc'>
      <li class='mb-2'>Auctions last for 30 minutes</li>
      <li class='mb-2'>The auction is only over when time is up</li>
      <li class='mb-2'>Accept any new offer to reject the current winner</li>
      <li class='mb-2'>You will only see the currently accepted offer, and the first offer received that has not been responded to</li>
      <li class='mb-2'>When an auction ends, you and the winner will receive game information to finish the trade</li>
      <li class='mb-2'>All auctions require moderation before becoming searchable/active</li>
      <li class='mb-2'>Upload an image of the in game item you wish to trade</li>
      <li class='mb-2 font-bold text-red-500'>NO REAL WORLD ITEMS CAN BE TRADED</li>
      <li class='mb-2 font-bold text-green-500'>Be kind and hae fun</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class='w-full'>
    <%= render "form", auction_item: @auction_item %>
  </div>
</div>